{
  "stem": "490.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So how can you explain somebody-- how would you understand?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So how would you-- can you understand if there is such a thing as somebody who created everything?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Einstein, and the Moon, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So how could you say, well, if I don't understand what God is, there is God.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, how would you be-- how could you expect to understand something what's so complicated, and it's so-- it's so-- everything, every move is so complicated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So-- and this is while we're trying to-- the strength what it gave me during the war was-- we were not only the-- the first ones to suffer.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And maybe there was a purpose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe there is-- in there is the hope for tomorrow, the hope that things might change, and there might be a future for us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, it is a-- as I said, religious convictions-- religious strength.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not only-- it's very difficult to be-- to be logic about things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's black and white, or whatever color.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's not that simple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You've got to have it in your-- you've got to live it through and to see as you go on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was the strength that you were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not only did I witness, but I-- I had my closest friends-- my closest-- the-- the really people that I thought that I knew that they-- they were real, strong people, people with quality, people which they were-- to me, they were the future of generations.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were wiped out, without any-- no-- with the blink of an eye, just because somebody didn't like him, or somebody-- or because of this atrocities, what happened, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's very difficult to-- at the time, I never thought that my life-- would-- would-- why it would continue.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
